---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Prose">
  <div class="prose-hero">
    <div class="fig-text-card">
      <h1 class="prose-title">Gathering Figs</h1>
      <p class="prose-meta">A memory of Pappou and the garden</p>
      
      <div class="full-story">
        <p>My feet were carefully placed in the stable crevices of the long smooth limbs of the tree; while I was normally scared of heights, the feeling of something alive supporting me gave me comfort...</p>
        <p>The rest of the figs are destined to be cut in halves and organized on a long wooden board to dry and wrinkle in the sun. These figs are the ones that would be nestled in our suitcase and flown back to New York. But I knew that it wasn't time yet to go back to New York. I placed the basket on the table and rushed outside; Pappou and I had more treasures to collect from his garden.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background-image: url('/figtree.jpeg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .fig-text-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 4rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .prose-title { font-size: 4rem; text-align: center; color: var(--deep-teal); }
  .prose-meta { text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .full-story p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
</style>